jrlCIRdynamicsJRLJapan::appariement

jrlCIRdynamicsJRLJapan::appariement Struct Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Binding structure:
  • corps is the body to which this structure belongs.

This should be equal to one of the field indexCorps1 or indexCorps of the internalLink's instance indicated by the field liaison.

  • liaison is the corresponding link.

The equality operator is used with the find function of <algorithm>.
